W. Szal et al. :

"The Rainforest Foundation is an organization that supports indigenous land
stewards to protect their ancestral forests. Regen Network is supporting Rainforest Foundation in leveraging the Global Forest Watch system of satellite
monitoring to give information to on-the-ground land stewards about potential
threats. Regen Network will serve as the public ledger for data and contracts to
streamline this operation and eventually payments will also flow through Regen
Network."
